In these Regulations - 

“2021 Annual Delegate Conference” shall be construed in accordance with 
Regulation 5; 

“Annual Delegate Conference” has the same meaning as it has in the 
Regulations of 1998; 

“Association” has the same meaning as it has in the Regulations of 1998; 

“district” has the same meaning as it has in the Regulations of 1998; 

“district committee” has the same meaning as it has in the Regulations of 1998; 

“Regulations of 1998” means the Garda Síochána (Associations) (Amendment) 
Regulations 1998 (S.I. No. 63 of 1998); 

“Special Delegate Conference” has the same meaning as it has in the 
Regulations of 1998; 

“Trustee” has the same meaning as it has in the Regulations of 1998. 

Notice of the making of this Statutory Instrument was published in 
“Iris Oifigiúil” of 23rd November, 2021. 








